# Pre-push: full quality gate before code reaches origin. `npm run verify`
# chains format:check -> lint -> typecheck -> test -> audit gate -> bare-marker
# grep, the same stages CI runs (see CICD-27 / CONTRIBUTING.md), so a green
# pre-push almost always means a green CI run.
#
# To skip in an emergency: `git push --no-verify`. Don't make this a habit.
npm run verify
